THIS PUBLICATION
relates to
the Public General Acts
and General Synod Measures
which received the Royal Assent in 1975
in which year ended the TWENTY- THIRD
and began the TWENTY- FOURTH YEAR
of the Reign of HER MAJESTY
QUEEN ELIZABETH THE SECOND
and
ended the First Session
and began the Second Session
of the Forty-Seventh Parliament of the
United Kingdom of Great Britain
and Northern Ireland .
