(6) The conditions mentioned in subsection (5 ) above are-
(a) that it appears to the Secretary of State that there is a
serious and immediate probability of the happening of
an event in relation to the company which would
constitute a change of control of the undertaking, or
( b) that the Secretary of State has learnt of circumstances
relating to the company which appear to him to con-
stitute a change of control of the undertaking on or
after 1st February 1975 .
