provisional notice is to be treated as requiring the information
specified in it to be furnished to the authorised representative
of each trade union within such reasonable time as may be speci-
fied in the notice under subsection ( 10) above.
(12) No such notice shall be given before the end of the
period specified in the provisional notice.
