authority or a development corporation, or any other body of
a public nature, on being so requested by the Agency, may place
the services of any of their staff at the Agency's disposal, on such
terms as may be agreed with the Agency.
6.- ( 1 ) The Agency may establish such committees for the Power to form
discharge of any of the Agency's functions, or for giving advice committees.
to the Agency about the discharge of any of their functions, as
