obtain
information.
c.70
Welsh Development Agency Act 1975
( 7 ) It shall be the duty of a person exercising powers conferred
by this section-
( a) to take reasonable care to avoid injury to plant,
machinery, equipment, livestock, crops or enclosures,
and
( b) on leaving any land, to secure it as effectively against
