Suspension from work on medical grounds PART II
29.-( 1 ) An employee who is suspended from work by his Right to
employer on medical grounds in consequence of- remuneration
on suspension
(a) any requirement imposed by or under any provision of on medical
any enactment or of any instrument made under any grounds.
enactment, or
