in respect of a day shall go towards discharging any liability
of the employer to pay contractual remuneration in respect of
that day.
( 5) For the purposes of Part II of Schedule 4 to this Act as
it applies for the calculation of a week's pay for the purposes
of this section, the calculation date is the last day on which the
employee worked under the contract of employment in force
immediately before the beginning of her absence.
