44.-( 1 ) Where the Secretary of State makes a payment to an
employee in respect of unpaid maternity pay in a case falling
within section 43 ( 1 )(a) above and it appears to the Secretary of
State that the employer's default in payment was without reason-
able excuse, the Secretary of State may recover from the
employer such amount as the Secretary of State considers appro-
