( 6 ) Where in the case of an employee the effective date of
termination is after the specified anniversary the amount of the
basic award calculated in accordance with subsections (3) to
( 5) above shall be reduced by the appropriate fraction.
( 7 ) In subsection ( 6 ) above " the specified anniversary " in
relation to a man means the 64th anniversary of the day of his
birth, and in relation to a woman means the 59th anniversary
of the day of her birth, and " the appropriate fraction " means
the fraction of which-
( a ) the numerator is the number of whole months reckoned
from the specified anniversary in the period beginning
with that anniversary and ending with the effective date
of termination ; and
( b) the denominator is 12.
