effect in relation to industrial tribunal proceedings, or claims
which could be the subject of tribunal proceedings, -
( a) arising out of a contravention, or alleged contravention,
of the following provisions of this Act, that is to say,
sections 22, 29, 35, 53, 57, 58, 59, 61, 70, 81, 99 and
