tal, supplementary or transitional provisions as appear to the
authority exercising the power to be necessary or expedient.
( 4 ) Any such power to make an order shall, except in the
case of an order made under Part III of this Act, include power
to revoke or vary the order by a subsequent order made under
that provision.
