1. For paragraph (1) of clause 8 of the model clauses set out in
Schedule 4 to the Petroleum (Production) Regulations 1966 as
amended by the Petroleum (Production) (Amendment) Regulations
"
1971 (hereafter in this Part of this Schedule referred to as the
relevant clauses " ) there shall be substituted the following
paragraph : -
