saved in the licensed area includes both petroleum in
the form of gas and petroleum in other forms, that
paragraph shall have effect-
(a) in relation to the petroleum in the form of gas,
as if references to petroleum in the provisions
of that paragraph relating to the meaning of
A and B excluded petroleum in other forms ;
and
