the aggregate exceed a quantity specified in the notice ;
( c ) shall not specify as a place at which delivery is to be made
in pursuance of the notice a place which is neither a well
head in the licensed area nor a point on land at which the
Licensee normally lands petroleum of any kind from that
area.
