given.
( 4) In this clause-
" completion work ", in relation to a well, means work, by way
of the installation of a casing or equipment or otherwise
after the well has been drilled, for the purpose of bringing
the well into use as a development well ; and
" development well " means a well which the Licensee uses or
intends to use in connection with the getting of petroleum
in the licensed area, other than a well which for the time
being he uses or intends to use only for searching for
petroleum.
