logical plans and maps relating to the licensed area and such other
records in relation thereto as may be necessary to preserve all infor-
mation which the Licensee has about the geology of the licensed area .
( 3) The Licensee shall deliver copies of the said records, plans and
maps referred to in the two foregoing paragraphs to the Minister as
and when required.
