policy of a company in financial difficulties which was a United
Kingdom policy at the relevant time as defined by section 16(6)
above, that the benefits provided for thereunder are or may
be excessive in any respect, having regard to the premiums
paid or payable and to any other terms of the policy, the Board
shall refer the policy to an independent actuary.
