reduced for the purposes there mentioned, subsection (2)( a)
above shall apply in relation to the policy as if the amount of
that benefit or (as the case may be) of any liability representing
that benefit, as reduced in accordance with the Board's deter-
mination, were the amount which would otherwise have been
payable in accordance with the terms of the policy.
