PART III
1961 с. 33.
1963 с. 51 .
1975 с. 24.
hardship tribunals under this section may, notwith-
standing anything in section 25 above or in the Land
Compensation Act 1961 or the Land Compensation
( Scotland) Act 1963, obtain certificates of appropriate
alternative development under Part III of the said
Act of 1961 or Part IV of the said Act of 1963, for
