32.-( 1 ) The Secretary of State shall be entitled to assume for Assumptions
the purposes of this Part of this Act that any office building or
as to
occupation.
part of an office building as respects which the person for the
time being entitled to possession was rated under Schedule 1 to
the General Rate Act 1967 or section 24 of the Local Govern- 1967 c. 9.
