(11) So long as section 33( 2) of the Civil Aviation Act 1949 1949 c. 67.
(local land charges) remains in force it shall be for the Authority,
instead of the Secretary of State, to act thereunder as regards
any order or direction made or given by virtue of paragraph 4,
5 or 7 of Schedule 3 to this Act.
