THE AIRPORTS AUTHORITY ACT 1975 (с. 78)
TABLE OF DERIVATIONS
Note: The following abbreviations are used in this Table-
1965
= Airports Authority Act 1965 (1965 c. 16 )
1968
= Civil Aviation Act 1968 ( 1968 с. 61)
1968 ( N )
= National Loans Act 1968 (1968 с. 13)
1971 =
Civil Aviation Act 1971 (1971 с. 75 )
