2. The derivation column does not acknowledge-
( a ) the transfer of the functions of fishery boards to river
boards by the River Boards Act 1948;
( b ) the transfer of the functions of river boards to river
authorities by the Water Resources Act 1963 ;
( c ) the transfer of the functions of river authorities to water
authorities by the Water Act 1973 .
